README

- The build file for this project relies on an installation of ant that should
be located in ./ant1.6.2 . So as to not add yet another copy of ant to perforce,
I've omitted it. Please make the appropriate changes to the build file before
attempting to compile.

- See the FlexTasks page on the flexteam wiki for more info:

  http://flexteam.macromedia.com/flexwiki/index.php/FlexTasks
